title: Kendall Jenner reveals what supermodels REALLY eat as she goes backstage at NYFW
text:
Kendall Jenner reveals what supermodels REALLY eat as she goes backstage at NYFW The model snacked on a fast food meal with her sister Kim Kardashian in between shows Share Click to play Tap to play The video will start in 8 Cancel Play now Kendall & Bella eat McDonald's in between NYFW shows Share this video   Thank you for subscribing!   
Models often talk about all the food they eat, and how they do nothing special to work out (other than have a personal trainer, their own chef and excellent genes, of course). 
But Kendall Jenner literally put her mouth where her money is when she revealed the surprising snack she and other models were chowing down on in between shows at New York Fashion Week. 
Visiting older sister Kim Kardashian backstage after Kanye's Yeezy Season 5 show was finished, Kendall brought with her... McDonald's. Bella Hadid, Gigi Hadid and Kendall Jenner all go out for a cheeky Maccy D's (Photo: Splash News) 
The sisters sat and eat the greasy fast food along with Bella Hadid and her sister Gigi Hadid. 
"Look at these delivery girls!" Kim said on Snapchat as she showed Kendall and Bella bringing in the food. "They're so cute, these delivery girls." 
She then showed her followers a picture of their feast, featuring an empty carton of French fries, chicken nuggets, a cheeseburger and a huge cup of fizzy drink. The super-three all had on their makeup from an earlier show (Photo: Splash News) 
It comes after Kendall found herself at the centre of attention once again when she became the main attraction at New York Fashion Week. 
And proving she really is the model of the moment, the Keeping Up With The Kardashians star looked fierce as she glided down the runway at the Anna Sui show on Wednesday. 
Switching up her look, the designer had the model rock dark purple lips, dark eye make-up, and styled her hair in two neat buns. Kendall Jenner on the catwalk (Photo: Rex Features) She looked fierce as she stormed the runway (Photo: Rex Features) 
The upcoming collection featured lots of monochrome, bold prints and embellished necklines and hems. 
Last week, Kendall looked just as hot when she sashayed down the catwalk for La Perla, wearing a beautiful sheer shimmering gown that was one of the highlights of the show. Read More Kendall sported cute hair buns for her catwalk appearance (Photo: Rex Features) Earlier, she'd been the star of the La Perla show (Photo: Rex Features) The shimmering gown left little to the imagination (Photo: Rex Features) 
The intricately beaded gown was sheer enough to give a cheeky glimpse of Kendallâ€™s bottom. 
The Kardashian sister and reality star has made a big name for herself in the fashion world and is no stranger to showing off her figure on the catwalk, having modelled for the Victoria's Secret show two years in a row.
